,"meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  Spanish Jose, Juan, Ana, Carlos, Margarita, Mario, Sergio, Adela, Adriana, Amando, Aminta, Andres.","Spanish: variant of   Ortiz   or of Catalan <b>Ortes</b>, plural form of   Orta  ."]},{"name":"Urtiz","meanings":["Hispanic (mainly Mexico): altered form of Spanish   Ortiz  ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1354684,"age":27,"year":"1200","julianDay":2159351,"description":"The Christian territory controlled the Kingdoms of Aragon, Navarre, and Castile.","jurisdictionLevel":3}],"lifeSummary":"When Lope Ortiz de Zúñiga y Azagra Señor de Mendavia was born in 1173, in Zúñiga, Zuñiga, Nafarroa, Spain, his father, Diego RAMIREZ DIAZ, was 12 and his mother, Urraca Perez de Bureba Iñiguez López, was 14. He married Tercia Fernández de Santiago about 1208, in Spain. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. He died in 1239, at the age of 66."},"et":{"1173–1239":"1173–1239","1182–Male":"1182–Surnud","1182–Female":"1182–Surnud","1203–1270":"1203–1270","1203–Male":"1203–Surnud","1161–1230":"1161–1230","1159–1230":"1159–1230","1239":"1239","1203":"1203","1159":"1159","Abt 1179":"umbes 1179","1200":"1200","1230":"1230","1173":"1173","1161":"1161","Abt 1208":"umbes 1208","1270":"1270","1182":"1182","Zúñiga, Zúñiga, Navarra, España":"Zúñiga, Zuñiga, Nafarroa, Hispaania","Zúñiga, Navarre, Spain":"Zuñiga, Nafarroa, Hispaania",",, Spain":"Hispaania",",,, Spain":"Hispaania"},"fi":{"1173–1239":"1173–1239","1182–Male":"1182–Kuollut","1182–Female":"1182–Kuollut","1203–1270":"1203–1270","1203–Male":"1203–Kuollut","1161–1230":"1161–1230","1159–1230":"1159–1230","1239":"1239","1203":"1203","1159":"1159","Abt 1179":"noin 1179","1200":"1200","1230":"1230","1173":"1173","1161":"1161","Abt 1208":"noin 1208","1270":"1270","1182":"1182","Zúñiga, Zúñiga, Navarra, España":"Zúñiga, Zuñiga, Nafarroa, Espanja","Zúñiga, Navarre, Spain":"Zuñiga, Nafarroa, Espanja",",, Spain":"Espanja",",,, Spain":"Espanja"},"fr":{"1173–1239":"1173–1239","1182–Male":"1182–Décédé",